所有程序包的分层结构

程序包分层结构:
  • controller,
  • controller.implementation,
  • controller.servlets,
  • model,
  • model.DAO,
  • model.entity,
  • util,
  • util.functions,
  • view,
  • view.receivers

类分层结构

  • java.lang.Object
    • util.functions.Creator
    • javax.servlet.GenericServlet (implements java.io.Serializable, javax.servlet.Servlet, javax.servlet.ServletConfig)
      • javax.servlet.http.HttpServlet
        • controller.servlets.InitServlet
        • controller.servlets.LoginServlet
        • controller.servlets.RegisterServlet
    • util.functions.Loader
    • controller.implementation.LoginImpl (implements view.receivers.LoginReceiver)
    • model.Managers
    • view.Receivers
    • controller.implementation.RegisterImpl (implements view.receivers.RegisterReceiver)
    • model.entity.Society
    • util.Test
    • model.entity.User

接口分层结构

  • view.receivers.LoginReceiver
  • view.receivers.RegisterReceiver
  • model.DAO.SocietyDAO
  • model.DAO.UserDAO
  • view.receivers.WebAdministratorReceiver

注释类型分层结构

  • util.Attribute (implements java.lang.annotation.Annotation)
